          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">
            Learning Time with Timmy
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base mb-6 leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
            A gentle introduction to English through play, songs, and stories with our lovable character Timmy. Perfect for preschoolers taking their first steps in learning.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.1);">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" style="color: var(--bc-cta-pink);" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Learn through play and creativity</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.1);">
